room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room DC in Washington, D.C.
room_address: 409 7th St NW, Lower Level, Washington, DC 20004
room_description: DC is in danger from a prehistoric threat! It’s up to you and your team of seven to make sure the dinosaur clones don’t take down the Nation’s Capital. An evil corporation is cloning dinosaurs, and we are the prey. Avoid detection, stop the cloning process, don’t become lunch, and conquer Jurassic Escape.
